= Dragon Warrior III (NES) - ROM Map =

This is a preliminary ROM map for ''Dragon Warrior III'' (NES). DW3 is one of the largest NES RPGs, using mapper 4 (MMC3) with extensive bank switching.

== ROM Header ==
The ROM uses the [[iNES]] format header.

{| class="wikitable"
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00-03 || 4 || NES header signature ("NES" + $1a)
|-
| $04 || 1 || PRG ROM size (32 = 512KB)
|-
| $05 || 1 || CHR ROM size (32 = 256KB)
|-
| $06 || 1 || Flags 6 (mapper 4, battery backup)
|-
| $07 || 1 || Flags 7 (mapper high bits)
|-
| $08-0f || 8 || Padding/unused
|}

==Bank Layout==
